<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <title>Microsoft Surface Laptop Go</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../CSS/ProductDetailsStyles.css">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@100..900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>


</head>

<body>

<!--Main container to contain the 2 columns-->
<container class="container">

    <!--Left gallery-->
    <div class="left-column">
        <img src="../../Images/SurfaceLaptop/MicosoftSurfaceLaptop.png" class="thumbnail" id="ProductImg">

        <div class="small-img-row">
            <div class="small-img-col">
                <img src="../../Images/SurfaceLaptop/MicosoftSurfaceLaptop.png" width="100%" class="small-img">
            </div>
            <div class="small-img-col">
                <img src="../../Images/SurfaceLaptop/1.jpg" width="100%" class="small-img">
            </div>
            <div class="small-img-col">
                <img src="../../Images/SurfaceLaptop/2.jpg" width="100%" class="small-img">
            </div>
            <div class="small-img-col">
                <img src="../../Images/SurfaceLaptop/3.jpg" width="100%" class="small-img">
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <hr class="vertical-line"/>

    <!--Right product info and stuff-->
    <div class="right-column">
        <h1 class="name">Microsoft Surface Laptop Go 3</h1>
        <h3 class="price">Rs.100000</h3>

        <!--In stock/out of stock square thingy-->
        <div class="availability">In Stock</div>

        <!--Product details table-->
        <table class="info-table">
            <tr>
                <td>Brand</td>
                <td>Microsoft</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Model Name</td>
                <td>Surface Laptop Go</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Storage Capacity</td>
                <td>256 GB</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>CPU</td>
                <td>Intel Core i5</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Memory</td>
                <td>8 GB</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <div class="option-buttons">
            <button class="buy-now">Buy Now</button>
            <button class="add-to-cart">Add to Cart</button>
        </div>

        <div class="favourite">
            <i id="wishlist-icon" class="far fa-star"></i><p>Wishlist</p>
        </div>

        <p class="description">The Surface Laptop Go is a stylish and compact laptop designed for everyday use and on-the-go productivity. It features a 12.4-inch PixelSense touchscreen display that offers crisp visuals and responsive touch interaction. Powered by Intel processors, it delivers reliable performance for multitasking and running apps smoothly. The laptop boasts a sleek design with a lightweight build, making it easy to carry around. The keyboard is comfortable for typing, and the large precision trackpad ensures smooth navigation. With up to 13 hours of battery life, the Surface Laptop Go can keep up with your busy schedule all day long. It also includes security features such as Windows Hello for secure logins. Ideal for students and professionals alike, the Surface Laptop Go is a versatile and efficient device for work and entertainment.
        </p>
    </div>

</container>

<script src="../../JS/ProductDetailsScript.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
